## Environment Variables

Required in `.env` (see `.env.example`):

- `WANDB_API_KEY`: Weights & Biases API key
- `WANDB_ENTITY`: W&B team/user name
- `HF_TOKEN`: HuggingFace token (for private models/datasets)

